  },
  {
    "Date": "18-06-2026",
    "Time_ET": "02:30:00 PM",
    "Activity": "The Threat Intelligence team conducts an inbox log audit to generate an explicit inventory of all message files accessed or downloaded by the attacker during the hijack window."
  },
  {
    "Date": "18-06-2026",
    "Time_ET": "03:00:00 PM",
    "Activity": "The affected executive's laptop is recalled for physical forensic imaging to ensure that no localized side-channel malware or credential-sniffing packages were deployed."
  },
  {
    "Date": "18-06-2026",
    "Time_ET": "03:30:00 PM",
    "Activity": "Quality assurance teams run validation test sequences against the updated Entra ID policy to ensure that remote logins outside the corporate network cleanly trigger mandatory device compliance blocks."
